{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Maybe sixteen, she nods "yes" eagerly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHASE
{DIALOGUE}: Jack, I'll see you Monday on set.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: I won't be there.
{DIALOGUE}: They're toning down my profile.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PRINTING PRESS
