{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's very bad timing as Exley enters, comes face-to-face with them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: This is hatred.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Acting on impulse, Bud goes after Exley.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's a mauling.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Four vicious body shots.
