{DIALOGUE}: Yes.
{DIALOGUE}: But do you know?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUD
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah I know.
{DIALOGUE}: Patchett's running whores and judging by his address, probably something bigger on the side.
