{DIALOGUE}: Three Ithaca pumps, an empty box of double-ought buck and cash.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack spots them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Three shotguns on the passenger side floor, an empty box of shells and loose dollar bills.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: So long, Vice.
{DIALOGUE}: Badge of Honor, here I come.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CARLISLE
{DIALOGUE}: Fuck you, Vincennes.
{DIALOGUE}: It's our collar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Breuning actually has to restrain his partner.
