{DIALOGUE}: Quiet.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm ranking officer here.
{DIALOGUE}: We go as a team.
{DIALOGUE}: End of story.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. CORRIDOR - TEVERE HOTEL - DAY
