{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SECOND BEDROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another black, RAY COATES, passed out on mattress, sur- rounded by empty beer cans.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack sticks his .38 in his back, starts to cuff him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As the cuff ratchets down...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. OBSERVATION ROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dudley watches intently as Ed Exley skims a report, memorizing names and dates.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack and other brass are also here along with a stenographer.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: So's Bud.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One of these guys killed Stensland.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Through tinted glass, the three suspects in three different rooms.
