{DIALOGUE}: Was she a hooker?
{DIALOGUE}: Hurt who?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: But Fontaine is gone.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Head lolling, eyes squeezing out tears.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OBSERVATION ROOM
