{DIALOGUE}: Is that right?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OBSERVATION ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Everyone's attention is riveted, particularly Bud's.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They watch, listen over the speaker.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EXLEY
{META_DATA}: (over speaker)
{DIALOGUE}: Kick loose, Jones.
{DIALOGUE}: I know you made her bleed, but that doesn't mean you killed her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No answer, but Jones is squirming.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EXLEY
