{DIALOGUE}: I think she's alive.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EXLEY
{META_DATA}: (over speaker)
{DIALOGUE}: You think?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack turns to Dudley.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: He's good.
{DIALOGUE}: I'll give him that.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They don't notice as the chair back begins to splinter in Bud's hands.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: #3 ROOM
