{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leaving the podium, Chase smiles at Ellis Loew's daughter who absolutely gushes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chase then winks knowingly to Jack who returns a tired, humorless smile.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack scans the room.
