{DIALOGUE}: And Reynolds?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
{DIALOGUE}: He's queer too.
{DIALOGUE}: Metro paid him two grand a week to fake it with ingenues.
{DIALOGUE}: On screen and off.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm getting him to fuck the D.A. for a hundred bucks.
{META_DATA}: (winks)
{DIALOGUE}: That's twice the fifty you got for wrecking his career.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Even Jack's not immune to a comment like that.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
{DIALOGUE}: Matt!
{DIALOGUE}: Over here!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Hudgeons heads over, Hudgeons points out...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
{DIALOGUE}: That's D.A. Loew right there.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reynolds gets a nervous bead on Loew.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hudgeons realizes:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
