{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reynolds, plae, nods at Jack.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REYNOLDS
{DIALOGUE}: Have we met before?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
