{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
{DIALOGUE}: Me neither.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reynolds looks like he's going to cry.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hudgeons returns with a double Scotch straight up and a hot dog with sauerkraut.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hands the drink to Matt.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
