{DIALOGUE}: Hey, it's not like you don't know how.
{DIALOGUE}: And Jack here has connections on 'Badge of Honor.'
{DIALOGUE}: Pull this off and there'll be a part for you.
{DIALOGUE}: I smell a comeback.
{DIALOGUE}: Don't you, Jack?
