{DIALOGUE}: And he's invested in freeway construction so he's gonna get a lot richer.
{DIALOGUE}: But that's it.
{DIALOGUE}: Patchett's what I like to call 'Twilight.'
{DIALOGUE}: He ain't queer, he ain't Red, he can't help me in my quest for prime sinuendo.
