{DIALOGUE}: And no one'll know about this?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: It'll be our secret.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: REYNOLDS
{DIALOGUE}: Showbiz.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Emboldened by Jack's promise, Reynolds heads off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack and Hudgeons watch as he strikes a conversation with Loew who's captivated.
