{DIALOGUE}: Let me get my camera.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hudgeons starts away, but Jack grabs him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Loew didn't go with him.
{DIALOGUE}: You're sure?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HUDGEONS
{DIALOGUE}: I put Reynolds in the cab myself.
{DIALOGUE}: The night cost me a hundred scoots and I got bupkis.
