{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUD
{DIALOGUE}: I got a few Nite Owl questions.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PINKER
{DIALOGUE}: I don't know if you read the papers, but that case is closed.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUD
{DIALOGUE}: I'm tying up loose ends.
{DIALOGUE}: Padding my report.
{DIALOGUE}: You know how it goes.
