{DIALOGUE}: Charges got dropped.
{DIALOGUE}: Insufficient evidence.
{DIALOGUE}: You were supervising officer on the case and I was wondering if you remember anything about it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DUDLEY
{DIALOGUE}: What's this all about, lad?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
