{DIALOGUE}: I fucked something up and I want to make amends.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DUDLEY
{META_DATA}: (smiles, then...)
{DIALOGUE}: Don't start trying to do the right thing, John.
{DIALOGUE}: You haven't had enough practice.
