{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He makes a dash for the door.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. VICTORY MOTEL - ROOM SIX - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sid Hudgeons is cuffed to the hot seat.
