{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She doesn't start crying till Bud turns and runs back into the rain.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. RECORDS ROOM - LAPD - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Drawers are open.
