{DIALOGUE}: On what evidence?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: EXLEY
{DIALOGUE}: None.
{DIALOGUE}: Call it a hunch.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LOEW
{META_DATA}: (incredulous)
