{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bud enters full of menace followed by Exley.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LOEW
{DIALOGUE}: Unless you're here to wipe my ass, I think we're through.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bud just glares at him.
